SLDNamedLayer1_0_0
public abstract class SLDNamedLayer
extends AbstractSLDLayer

Implements the NamedLayer element of an SLD implementation specification.

A named layer is a layer that can be accessed from an OpenGIS Web Server using a well-known name.

Author:
pepe vidal salvador - jose.vidal.salvador@iver.es
